We are destroying the very means by which life is extended.

8
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:27,760
每一次全球性的瘟疫灾难都可以被归咎
Every single global ill that plagues the Earth can be traced back...

9
00:01:27,790 --> 00:01:31,530
被归咎于人口的过剩 人口过剩
traced back to human overpopulation... human overpopulation.

10
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,240
