Maybe pain can save us.

18
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:05,670
有一个开关
There is a switch,

19
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:09,120
若你打开
if you throw it,

20
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:12,910
地球上半数人口会死亡
half the people on earth will die.

21
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:19,880
但反之 人类将在一百年内灭绝
But if you don't, the human race will be extinct in a hundred years.

22
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,500
你会怎么做
What would you do?

23
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:31,100
人类就像人体内的癌症
Mankind is the cancer in its own body.

24
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:35,600
