The hardest one yet.

28
00:02:45,610 --> 00:02:48,580
坎坷尽头 横亘炼狱
Inferno will be at the end

29
00:02:48,940 --> 00:02:52,190
你是我的应急计划
You are my contingency plan.

30
00:02:52,220 --> 00:02:55,680
你是人类最后的希望
You are humanity's final hope.

31
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:59,830
