所有希望
All hope ...

52
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:44,650
兰登先生 我是布鲁克斯医生
Mr. Langdon, I'm Dr. Brooks.

53
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:48,150
我会做些检查 不必担心
I'm going to do a few checks, nothing to worry about.

54
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,960
咱们把它扔掉 好吗
Let's get rid of this, shall we?

55
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:00,900
您知道今天是周几吗
Do you know what day of the week it is?

56
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:03,250
周六
Saturday.

57
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:07,160
今天周一 6月28号
It's Monday, 28th of June.

58
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,810
周一 6月28号
Monday, 28th of June.

59
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,780
您知道我们在哪儿吗
Do you know where we are?

60
00:06:12,730 --> 00:06:14,350
波士顿
Boston.

61
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:18,100
麻省总医院
Massachusetts General (Hospital)

62
00:06:19,370 --> 00:06:23,200
您最后能记起的事情是什么
And what's the last thing you can remember?

63
00:06:25,650 --> 00:06:28,840
我 呃 我在校园里
I uh... I was on campus.

64
