Was I in some kind of an accident?

66
00:06:40,690 --> 00:06:42,570
我们会弄清楚的
We'll get to that.

67
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,380
您有没有人需要帮忙通知的
Is there someone we should call for you?

68
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:46,570
没
No.

69
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,220
您的妻子 家人
Your Wife? Family?

70
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:52,320
不 不 我没结婚
No. No. I'm not married.

71
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:56,530
兰登教授 你的头部受创
Professor Langdon, you're suffering from a head trauma.

72
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:59,530
您似乎有轻微的逆行性失忆
You appeared to have a mild retrograde amnesia

73
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:02,800
