We've done a CT scan, there's no evidence of intracranial bleeding.

74
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:06,570
一切都挺好 会恢复的
Which is very reassuring. Non-terminal.

75
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:08,840
试着放松下来
Just try to relax.

76
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:11,240
神经系统方面 看样子没问题
Neurologically, you seem to be fine.

77
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:13,920
您的记忆会在随后几天恢复
Your memory will return over the next several days.

78
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:17,050
那么我们 ... 我们就安心静养吧
So we'll... we'll wait and watch.

79
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,880
能麻烦你关下灯吗
Could you turn off the lights please.

80
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,640
没问题
Of course.

81
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:25,490
若是头部创伤严重 导致脑挫裂伤 那...
If the head trauma was bad enough to cause a cerebral contusion, then...

82
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:28,570
麻烦你 ... 麻烦你关下灯好吗
Could you please ... Could you please turn off the lights?

83
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:36,250
我在 ... 佛罗伦萨 ... 来干什么
What am I... doing... in Florence?

84
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:41,760
那是个大教堂 是佛罗伦萨旧宫 对吗
That's a Duomo. That's the Palazzo Vecchio, isn't it?

85
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:43,000
对的
Yes.

86
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:46,560
怎么 ... 我怎么来这儿的
How... How did I get here?

87
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:50,350
3小时前 你头部带伤 跑来我们的急诊室
You came to our emergency room 3 hours ago with a head wound.

88
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:58,850
我 ... 我是不是还有位女伴
Was I... Was I with a woman?

89
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:01,140
没 一位出租车司机送您来的
No, a cab driver brought you in.

90
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:05,420
没拿钱包 没有手机 没带身份证
No wallet. No phone. No ID.

91
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:08,230
你怎么知道我名字
How do you know my name?

92
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:11,210
咱俩见过
We've met.

93
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:15,440
我在伦敦帝国学院听过你的演讲 后面还聊了下
I saw you lecture at the Church in Imperial College London, we spoke afterwards,

94
00:08:16,130 --> 00:08:18,290
您待我很亲切
you were very nice to me.

95
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:19,850
我们见过
We've met.

96
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,500
抱歉 那样讲不大恰当
Sorry, that's not quite fair.

97
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:24,260
那时候我9岁
I was nine at that time.

98
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:26,810
慢着 9 9岁
Wait. Nine-nine years old?

99
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:28,950
我那时对拼图游戏很入迷
I was crazy about puzzles.

100
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:32,170
我也喜欢您的书
And I like your books.

101
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:37,090
也许不是"失落的表意文字语言" 而是其他的
Maybe not "Lost language of Ideograms", but the others.

102
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:38,650
好吧
Okay.

103
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:40,460
我全看了
I read them all.

104
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:43,000
古怪的小年轻
A weird kid.

105
00:08:44,330 --> 00:08:46,330
的确如此
I was actually.

106
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:49,160
我刚刚讲得很大声吗
Did I say that out loud?

107
00:08:49,190 --> 00:08:50,730
是的
You did.

108
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,500
非常抱歉
Very sorry.

109
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:06,720
兰登教授 您的头疼症状一开始会比较强烈
Professor Langdon, your headaches are going to be intense initially.

110
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:10,690
您也可能还会有恶心 糊涂 头昏等情况
And you can also expect nausea, confusion and dizziness.

111
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,440
前台来的电话
That was the front desk.

112
00:09:26,890 --> 00:09:29,210
警察来了 要见您
The police are here to see you.

113
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:30,860
我 为什么
Me, why?

114
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:34,380
在与他们交流之前 兰登教授 您应该了解一下您的真实情况
Before you talk to them, Professor Langdon, you should know the facts of your case.

115
00:09:34,410 --> 00:09:36,160
您头部的创伤并非事故所致
Your head wound was not caused by an accident.

116
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:38,180
而是枪击造成的
It was the result of a gunshot.

117
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,140
一枚子弹擦过您头骨顶端 您很可能还狠狠地摔了下来
A bullet grazed the top of your skull and you most likely took a bad fall

118
00:09:41,170 --> 00:09:42,830
这是导致脑震荡的原因
which is what caused the concussion.

119
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:45,440
如果子弹再往里一英吋
If the bullet had been an inch to the side,

120
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:48,130
它就真的要命了
it could have killed you.

121
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:21,500
快点 快点儿
Come on, Come on

122
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:42,110
这边 这边 快
This way. This way, come on.

123
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:16,440
出租车
Taxi.

124
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,870
进来
Get in.

125
