啥 你们喝醉了吗
What, are you drunk?

126
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:32,000
怎么回事
What happened?

127
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,700
快走
Let's go!

128
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,500
加速 开快点
Step on it. Floor it!

129
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,900
- 出了啥事 - 我不知道
- What's going on? - I don't know

130
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:48,040
接下来会比较疼
This is gonna hurt.

131
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,970
没关系
It's okay. It's okay.

132
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,900
罗伯特
Robert.

133
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:02,610
寻找 就寻见
Seek and find.

134
