I don't know.

144
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:19,500
还有 你进急诊室时
Also, when you came into ER,

145
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:21,790
你在反覆喃喃些什么
you were mumbling something over and over.

146
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:27,240
非常抱 ... 非常抱歉
Very sorr... Very sorry.

147
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:30,240
非常抱歉
Very sorry.

148
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,490
你知道你当时为什么要讲这些吗
Do you have any idea why you would be saying this?

149
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:43,110
- 不知道 - 为什么有人要射杀你
- No. - Why was someone shooting at you?

150
00:13:43,130 --> 00:13:45,600
你可以继续对我追问这些 女士
You can keep asking me these questions, lady.

151
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,500
但我也不知道答案是什么
But I'm not going to know these answers!

152
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,900
我叫西恩娜
My name is Sienna.

153
