对不起
I'm sorry.

154
00:13:55,530 --> 00:13:56,990
你好
Hello.

155
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,350
你好
Hi.

156
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:01,500
你刚刚问了很多问题
You just asked a lot of questions.

157
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:03,620
没错 我感觉我现在非常玻璃心
Yeah, I'm feeling a tad vulnerable right now.

158
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:06,710
我现在身旁待着一个正被追杀的人
I'm with someone other people want to shoot at!

159
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,540
对不起
I'm sorry.

160
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:12,410
这些问题很重要
Questions are important.

161
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,320
我希望你能记起来
And I hope you recover.

162
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:19,840
我可以再要 ... 一杯
Can I ask you for a... cup of a...

163
00:14:24,730 --> 00:14:28,030
