People drink it in the morning for energy. Uh...

165
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:32,390
茶
Tea.

166
00:14:32,410 --> 00:14:34,330
茶 不 另一种
Tea. No. The other one.

167
00:14:34,350 --> 00:14:36,240
- 咖啡 - 咖啡
- Coffee. - Coffee.

168
00:14:36,410 --> 00:14:38,770
我能要一杯咖啡吗
Could I have a cup of coffee?

169
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:41,180
当然
Sure.

170
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,050
谢谢
Thank you.

171
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:51,040
你整理得很好
You are very organized.

172
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:53,630
我喜欢井井有条的样子
I like things tidy.

173
00:14:54,570 --> 00:14:57,940
谢谢你在医院里的帮助
Thank you for helping me in the hospital.

174
00:14:57,970 --> 00:15:00,040
