And only fifty years to double again to four billion people in 1970.

345
00:26:48,530 --> 00:26:52,520
现在 我们快有80亿了
We're nearly at eight billion now.

346
00:26:52,650 --> 00:26:57,010
巴特利特以烧杯为例 (巴特利特：英国化学家)
Bartlett used the example of a beaker.

347
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:58,570
内有一个细菌细胞
With a single bacterium.

348
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:01,920
每分钟分裂一次 数目翻倍
One that divides and doubles every minute.

349
00:27:01,950 --> 00:27:05,660
如果在11点整将第一个细菌细胞置于杯中
If you placed the first bacterium into the beaker at 11 o'clock.

350
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:09,010
12点整时杯就全满了
and it's completely full by 12.

351
00:27:09,040 --> 00:27:13,250
在何时烧杯还是半满的呢
At what time is the beaker still only half full?

