862
01:06:38,010 --> 01:06:40,630
我已经追捕贝特朗·佐布里斯特两年了
I've been chasing Bertrand Zobrist for 2 years.

863
01:06:40,660 --> 01:06:44,330
一直有人在竭力反对我
And someone has been working against me.

864
01:06:46,610 --> 01:06:49,670
咱们讲重点 你知道病毒在哪里吗
Let's get to the point. You know where the virus is?

865
01:06:49,700 --> 01:06:52,620
我猜你应该有身份证明吧
I assume you have some sort of credentials.

866
01:06:52,990 --> 01:06:54,760
要问WHO的话你请便
Call WHO if you like.

867
01:06:54,780 --> 01:06:57,750
查一下我 但动作快点
Check me out, but do it quickly.

868
01:07:02,310 --> 01:07:04,630
威尼斯 我觉得在威尼斯
Venice. We think it's Venice.

869
01:07:04,650 --> 01:07:05,860
很好
Good.

870
01:07:05,880 --> 01:07:08,110
坐火车要两小时 跟我来吧
It's 2 hours by train. Come on.

871
01:07:08,140 --> 01:07:10,990
如果我能找到你 别人也可以
If I could find you, so can the others.

872
01:07:11,880 --> 01:07:14,340
我给你们都买张去日内瓦的机票
I'm buying you both plane tickets to Geneva.

873
01:07:14,360 --> 01:07:16,920
不 不是日内瓦 他说是威尼斯
No, not Geneva. He said Venice.

874
01:07:16,950 --> 01:07:18,590
我听到了
I heard that.

875
01:07:21,290 --> 01:07:23,320
让一下 请大家注意
Excuse us. Please watch yourselves.

876
01:07:23,340 --> 01:07:26,200
请退后 让一下
Step back, please. Excuse us.

877
01:07:27,030 --> 01:07:28,520
让一下
Excuse us.

878
01:07:29,380 --> 01:07:31,090
请大家注意
Watch yourself, please.

879
01:07:31,110 --> 01:07:34,770
- 这是飞日内瓦的班机吗 - 是的 不过登机口刚刚关闭了
- This is the plane to Geneva? - Yes, but we just closed the door.

880
01:07:34,790 --> 01:07:37,790
让飞机待那别动 我们要检查全部乘客
Keep the plane at the gate. We need to check every passenger.

881
01:07:37,810 --> 01:07:40,190
那就是在浪费时间了
That would be a waste of time.

882
01:07:40,480 --> 01:07:42,500
而且我们的时间很紧
And we have very little of that.

883
01:07:43,250 --> 01:07:46,450
前往威尼斯的Italo 9982次动车 下午 1:57

884
01:07:53,100 --> 01:07:57,660
三天前 在历经两年的追查后 我们找到了佐布里斯特
3 days ago, after 2 years of searching, I found Zobrist.

885
01:07:57,680 --> 01:08:01,480
他然后自杀了 但我们在他口袋里找到一个包裹
He killed himself. But we took a package from his pocket.

886
01:08:01,510 --> 01:08:02,690
里面是什么
And what was in it?

887
01:08:02,710 --> 01:08:05,690
装有"地狱图"的法拉第指示器
The Faraday pointer with the map of hell.

888
01:08:05,710 --> 01:08:10,300
是一个谜题 专门为其拥护者解谜而设计的
A puzzle, specifically designed for his followers to solve.

889
01:08:10,330 --> 01:08:11,950
我们把它交给了你
We brought it to you.

890
01:08:11,970 --> 01:08:13,750
你正在解密的时候
And you were in the process of decoding it,

891
01:08:13,780 --> 01:08:15,690
被人给绑架了
when you were kidnapped.

892
01:08:17,770 --> 01:08:19,900
兰登教授
Professor Langdon.

893
01:08:26,240 --> 01:08:30,260
- 你当时跟辛斯基博士在一块 - 伊丽莎白 对的
- You were with Dr. Sinskey at the time. - Elizabeth, yes.

894
01:08:30,280 --> 01:08:34,480
她有没有向你透露任何对病毒感兴趣的第三方组织
Did she tell you about any third party interest in the virus?

895
01:08:36,280 --> 01:08:39,170
- 不记得了 - 她在经济上是不是有困难
- I don't remember. - Did she have financial problems?

896
01:08:39,190 --> 01:08:40,340
呃 我不知道
Uh, I don't know.

897
01:08:40,360 --> 01:08:41,980
她有没有带着备用手机
Did she carry more than one cellphone?

898
01:08:42,010 --> 01:08:42,960
不知道
I don't know.

899
01:08:42,990 --> 01:08:44,090
- 想一下 - 他不记得了
- Think. - He doesn't remember.

900
01:08:44,120 --> 01:08:49,580
那就告诉我谁能记得 教授 "不知道 不记得" 真是够了
Then tell me who can remember, Professor! Enough with the "I don't know, I don't remember."!

901
01:08:49,600 --> 01:08:51,530
这样对他不好
It's not good for him.

902
01:08:53,210 --> 01:08:55,870
那个"金碧辉煌的博学园"是在威尼斯圣马可大教堂内
The "gilded museum" is that Saint Mark's.

903
01:08:55,900 --> 01:08:57,690
整个威尼斯都是博学园
All of Venice is a museum.

904
01:08:57,720 --> 01:09:02,190
那儿有"圣马尔谷之马"雕塑 它们都是铜像
St. Mark's has the Horses of Constantinople, they're bronze statues.

905
01:09:02,220 --> 01:09:04,020
我可以看看吗
Can I see that?

906
01:09:07,880 --> 01:09:09,790
是我我就不会碰它
I wouldn't touch it.

907
01:09:09,810 --> 01:09:11,950
我也不打算那样
I wasn't planning on it.

908
01:09:20,100 --> 01:09:21,630
教授
Professor.

909
01:09:23,820 --> 01:09:25,600
兰登教授
Professor Langdon.

910
01:09:25,630 --> 01:09:27,330
兰登教授
Professor Langdon.

911
01:09:27,410 --> 01:09:29,380
兰登教授
Professor Langdon.

912
01:09:30,340 --> 01:09:32,100
是我
Yes.

913
01:09:33,330 --> 01:09:35,270
你好 罗伯特
Hello, Robert.

914
01:09:37,360 --> 01:09:39,150
伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

915
01:09:39,330 --> 01:09:41,640
好久不见
It's been a long time.

916
01:09:45,720 --> 01:09:47,620
太久了
Too long.

917
01:09:49,540 --> 01:09:51,480
是什么风把你吹来了
What brings you here?

918
01:09:53,260 --> 01:09:56,080
WHO需要你的帮助
The WHO needs your help.

919
01:09:56,640 --> 01:09:57,750
我的帮助
My help?

920
01:09:57,770 --> 01:10:00,270
我希望你还记得但丁
I hope you still remember your Dante.

921
01:10:03,800 --> 01:10:05,620
刚刚发生了什么
What just happened?

922
01:10:11,210 --> 01:10:12,930
你还好吗
Are you alright?

923
01:10:12,950 --> 01:10:15,810
你能弄点水吗 他可能脱水了
Could you get some water? He could be dehydrated.

924
01:10:15,830 --> 01:10:19,840
弄点吃的 或者水果 或者列车上别的什么
Some food, maybe some fruit or something from the machine.

925
01:10:19,860 --> 01:10:21,740
- 快点 - 好的
- Quickly. - Sure.

926
01:10:21,760 --> 01:10:23,290
谢谢
Thank you.

927
01:10:31,300 --> 01:10:33,920
- 他在撒谎吗 - 他在撒谎
- Is he lying? - Through his teeth.

928
01:10:33,950 --> 01:10:36,950
他不是那天来找我的人
He was not the one who came to Cambridge to see me.

929
01:10:49,820 --> 01:10:54,290
布沙尔 快来帮我 快点 我觉得他虚脱了
Bouchard, I need help, quickly. I think he's collapsed.

930
01:11:03,590 --> 01:11:05,680
这门我打不开
I can't open the door.

931
01:11:07,130 --> 01:11:08,700
兰登
Langdon?

932
01:11:09,460 --> 01:11:11,040
你还好吗
Are you okay?

933
01:11:12,910 --> 01:11:14,860
兰登 你还好吗
Langdon, are you okay?

934
01:11:26,750 --> 01:11:28,360
快点 咱们走
Come on, let's go!

935
01:11:33,740 --> 01:11:35,430
你在告诉我过去两年来
You're telling me that for 2 years,

936
01:11:35,450 --> 01:11:38,680
你和你的组织都在跟我作对吗
you and your organization have been working against me.

937
01:11:38,710 --> 01:11:39,840
没错
That is correct.

938
01:11:39,870 --> 01:11:42,430
掩饰贝特朗·佐布里斯特和他的研究
To shield Bertrand Zobrist and his research.

939
01:11:42,450 --> 01:11:45,750
- 藏着他 保护他 - 很遗憾 是的
- To hide him, to protect him. - Regrettably, yes.

940
01:11:45,780 --> 01:11:49,130
而我全部的 避免他引发全球性流行病的尝试
And that all of my attempts to prevent him from initiating

941
01:11:49,160 --> 01:11:53,280
都因为你们在从中作梗而失败了
a worldwide pandemic have failed because of you.

942
01:11:53,310 --> 01:11:55,700
简单概括的话 是的
An incisive sum-up, yes.

943
01:11:55,730 --> 01:12:01,960
现在你又冒冒失失的跑来 要求我相信你
Now you have the temerity to ask that I simply decide to trust you?

944
01:12:01,990 --> 01:12:06,320
非常抱歉 在我看来 别无他法
I'm terribly sorry, I didn't see any other way.

945
01:12:09,810 --> 01:12:13,710
你的团队 到底是干什么的
Who exactly does your group work for?

946
01:12:16,710 --> 01:12:18,820
当然是服务于客户
Our clients, of course.

947
01:12:18,840 --> 01:12:23,000
我们是一家私人安保公司 运作得很成功
We are a private security firm. A very successful one.

948
01:12:23,030 --> 01:12:24,890
我可以请问一下
May I ask,

949
01:12:25,520 --> 01:12:28,850
之前与你共事的那位绅士 布沙尔探员
the gentleman who was with you, agent Bouchard,

950
01:12:29,470 --> 01:12:31,340
他现在在哪儿
where is he now?

951
01:12:32,640 --> 01:12:35,140
我们不得而知 他已经失去行踪了
We don't know. We lost track of him.

952
01:12:35,690 --> 01:12:38,040
那么现在的情况要比你们想像的还糟
Then the situation is worse than you think.

953
01:12:38,070 --> 01:12:40,880
只有唯一一种原因会令他选择失联
There is only one reason he would move out of contact,

954
01:12:40,910 --> 01:12:43,030
他想要独自找到兰登先生
he wants Mr. Langdon to himself.

955
01:12:43,060 --> 01:12:43,980
为什么
Why?

956
01:12:44,000 --> 01:12:47,180
找到病毒 然后再抬价转手 我猜的
To find the virus and sell it to the highest bidder I assume.

957
01:12:47,210 --> 01:12:50,290
借贷收购 敲诈勒索 你懂的 老一套
Leverage, blackmail, you know, the usual shit.

958
01:12:50,310 --> 01:12:53,450
我觉得咱们不必再深入讨论了 西姆斯先生
I don't think we have anything further to discuss, Mr. Sims.

959
01:12:53,470 --> 01:12:56,760
寻找病原体的时间已经不足8小时 抱歉
And I have less than 8 hours to find this pathogen, excuse me.

960
01:12:56,780 --> 01:13:01,030
据我所知 在此之前你就认识教授
From what I understand, you knew the Professor sometime ago.

961
01:13:02,920 --> 01:13:04,680
有过私交
Personally.

962
01:13:06,260 --> 01:13:08,290
你在乎他
You care about him.

963
01:13:09,460 --> 01:13:15,780
你甚至会为了保护他 而跟像我这种不择手段的人合作 不是吗
You would even ally with an unscrupulous character
such as myself to protect him, wouldn't you?

964
01:13:19,530 --> 01:13:23,650
我的组织就有找到兰登教授的资源
My organization has the resources to find your Professor.

965
01:13:44,000 --> 01:13:46,830
威尼斯 意大利 下午 2:49

966
01:13:50,880 --> 01:13:54,020
若你想要散播瘟疫 这儿就是理想之地
If you wanted to start a plague, this is where you do it.

967
01:13:54,050 --> 01:13:55,470
没错
Yep.

968
01:13:55,880 --> 01:13:59,730
这儿每年有两千万游客来自全球各地的游客
20 million people a year come here from every corner of the globe.

969
01:13:59,760 --> 01:14:03,700
14世纪黑死病肆虐期间 威尼斯人号令全部船只
During the Black Death, the Venetians made all the ships

970
01:14:03,720 --> 01:14:05,580
在港口抛锚停泊40天
anchored in the harbor for 40 days,

971
01:14:05,610 --> 01:14:07,680
随后才允许船员入城
before they would allow the crews into the city.

972
01:14:07,710 --> 01:14:10,620
以确保瘟疫不会传入城内
Making sure that they were not carrying the Plague.

973
01:14:10,650 --> 01:14:12,810
英文中"隔离"一词就是来自意大利语
The word "Quarantine" comes from the Italian.

974
01:14:12,840 --> 01:14:15,750
还有"四十" 来自"Quaranta"
"quaranta", "forty".

975
01:14:15,970 --> 01:14:18,610
有你陪同感觉很棒呢 教授
It's nice to have you back, Professor.

976
01:14:19,510 --> 01:14:23,260
那儿 马雕在那儿 (圣马尔谷之马)
There, the horses.

977
01:14:29,290 --> 01:14:33,260
都是复制品 原件在圣殿内部保管 (原因: 空气污染)
These were recreations, the originals are in a museum for preservation.

978
01:14:33,280 --> 01:14:36,400
得赶紧了 布沙尔知道我们会到这儿
We should be quick. Bouchard knows we are coming here.

979
01:14:37,390 --> 01:14:38,830
打扰一下
Excuse me.

980
01:14:39,310 --> 01:14:43,080
问一下那位导游 这些雕塑的马头有没有被切下过
Ask that guide, if the heads have ever been severed from these horses?

981
01:14:43,100 --> 01:14:46,140
打扰一下 打扰一下
Excuse me. Excuse me.

982
01:14:46,160 --> 01:14:47,990
- 打扰一下 - 麻烦了 打扰一下
- Excuse me. - Please excuse me.

983
01:14:48,010 --> 01:14:49,420
麻烦了
Please.

984
01:14:57,910 --> 01:14:59,600
传说在第四次十字军东征期间(1202年 - 1204年)
According to the tale, during the Crusades,

985
01:14:59,620 --> 01:15:02,650
这些马雕被威尼斯军队从拜占庭的君士坦丁堡(今伊斯坦布尔)劫走
the horses were looted from Constantinople.

986
01:15:05,790 --> 01:15:07,510
马匹...
Horses...

987
01:15:09,410 --> 01:15:12,460
但它们实在太大 难以装船
But they were too large to be loaded on board the ships,

988
01:15:14,540 --> 01:15:17,000
所以马头被切下 随后再重新接回
so their heads were removed and reattached.

989
01:15:17,020 --> 01:15:18,510
哪位总督干的
By whom?

990
01:15:18,950 --> 01:15:21,500
那位长生不老的总督 恩里科·丹多洛 (第41任威尼斯总督)
The doge who lived forever, Enrico Dandolo.

991
01:15:21,530 --> 01:15:24,390
- 恩里科·丹多洛 - 长生不老的总督
- Enrico Dandolo. - The doge who lived forever.

992
01:15:24,410 --> 01:15:26,000
当然了 恩里科·丹多洛
Of course, Enrico Dandolo.

993
01:15:26,030 --> 01:15:28,280
丹多洛把威尼斯人骗入十字军中
Dandolo tricked the Venetians into the Crusades.

994
01:15:28,310 --> 01:15:33,190
他原本应当率众前往埃及 却跑去把君士坦丁堡给洗劫了
He was supposed to sail his ships to Egypt, but he sacked Constantinople instead.

995
01:15:33,210 --> 01:15:35,350
我很抱歉 当然是他了
I'm sorry. Of course.

996
01:15:35,370 --> 01:15:37,970
"金碧辉煌的神圣智慧博学园"
"The gilded museum of holy wisdom."

997
01:15:39,000 --> 01:15:40,980
我们找错了教堂吗
Are we in the wrong basilica?

998
01:15:41,010 --> 01:15:43,080
我们找错了国家
We're in the wrong country.

999
01:15:43,720 --> 01:15:46,010
丹多洛逝世后 并没有埋葬在此
Dandolo passed, but he was not buried here.

1000
01:15:46,030 --> 01:15:47,650
那他葬在哪里
So where was he buried?

1001
01:15:47,680 --> 01:15:49,640
圣索菲亚大教堂
Hagia Sophia.

1002
01:15:49,940 --> 01:15:52,270
- 伊斯坦布尔 - 伊斯坦布尔 (土耳其)
- Istanbul. - Istanbul.

1003
01:16:38,400 --> 01:16:40,000
总会有出路的
There's always a way out.

1004
01:16:41,470 --> 01:16:43,020
在这儿 这儿
Here. Here.

1005
01:16:50,030 --> 01:16:52,100
看看你能不能把那个打开来
See if you could get that open.

1006
01:16:54,920 --> 01:16:56,670
我抓住你的脚了
I got your foot.

1007
01:17:12,700 --> 01:17:14,480
能搞定吗
Can you get it?

1008
01:17:27,750 --> 01:17:28,990
外头有人吗
Is there someone there?

1009
01:17:29,010 --> 01:17:30,860
请帮一下
Please help.

1010
01:17:36,260 --> 01:17:37,570
对 对
Yes.

1011
01:17:37,790 --> 01:17:39,430
拉我一把
Give me a hand.

1012
01:17:39,450 --> 01:17:41,750
- 100块 - 好的 好的
- One hundred. - Yes! Yes.

1013
01:17:41,770 --> 01:17:44,310
- 100欧元 - 给 我有 我有的
- A hundred euro. - Here. I got it. I got it.

1014
01:17:52,760 --> 01:17:54,340
快 快 快
Quick. Quick. Quick.

1015
01:18:16,260 --> 01:18:17,870
谢谢
Thank you.

1016
01:18:38,590 --> 01:18:40,130
你在干什么
What are you doing?

1017
01:18:41,450 --> 01:18:45,700
你说过他是个谋杀犯 是个精神变态
You called him a murderer, a psychopath.

1018
01:18:46,930 --> 01:18:48,300
什么
What?

1019
01:18:48,320 --> 01:18:51,410
但历史会把我们视为救世主
But history will call us saviors.

1020
01:18:53,920 --> 01:18:57,760
天呐 我的天呐
Oh my god. Oh my god.

1021
01:18:59,260 --> 01:19:01,640
我不怕死 罗伯特
I'm not afraid to die, Robert.

1022
01:19:04,760 --> 01:19:07,510
但无所事事才是令我害怕的
But doing nothing terrifies me.

1023
01:19:07,530 --> 01:19:12,720
指引 指示器 他是要留给你的 佐布里斯特
The path, and the pointer, he left that all for you, Zobrist.

1024
01:19:13,860 --> 01:19:17,010
- 你认识他吗 - 何止认识
- You knew him? - Knew him?

1025
01:19:17,400 --> 01:19:19,630
我爱他
I loved him.

1026
01:19:20,110 --> 01:19:22,550
你这套衣服就是他的
You're wearing his suit.

1027
01:19:23,410 --> 01:19:25,800
不 西恩娜 不
No. Sienna, no.

1028
01:19:25,830 --> 01:19:27,600
谢谢你 罗伯特
Thank you, Robert.

1029
01:19:30,020 --> 01:19:32,250
谢谢你做的一切
Thank you for everything.

1030
01:19:33,560 --> 01:19:37,350
不 不 西恩娜 不要
No. No. Sienna, no.

1031
01:19:38,040 --> 01:19:39,560
西恩娜
Sienna!

1032
01:19:40,100 --> 01:19:42,850
不 西恩娜 西恩娜 不要
No, Sienna! Sienna, no!

1033
01:20:11,040 --> 01:20:14,480
慢点 慢点 你太快啦
Slow down, slow down. You're too fast.

1034
01:20:37,070 --> 01:20:39,120
噢 拜托 拜托
Oh, come on. Come on.

1035
01:20:39,140 --> 01:20:41,390
这个费了我三天时间
This took me 3 days.

1036
01:20:41,410 --> 01:20:43,160
太简单啦
Too easy.

1037
01:20:43,190 --> 01:20:45,260
"镀金时代" - 马克·吐温
"The Gilded Age" by Mark Twain

1038
01:20:53,490 --> 01:20:55,140
我很喜欢
I love it.

1039
01:21:06,290 --> 01:21:09,280
认识你之前
Everything before you exist,

1040
01:21:10,880 --> 01:21:12,770
完美生活还是臆想
an idea.

1041
01:21:15,180 --> 01:21:17,160
如今已经成真了
And now it's real.

1042
01:21:19,310 --> 01:21:24,360
爱 让 灵魂 复苏
Love awaken the soul to act.

1043
01:21:29,090 --> 01:21:34,320
这可不公平 拿但丁来比喻我
That's not fair. Quoting Dante to me.

1044
01:21:36,810 --> 01:21:41,280
不过诗句里是"美" 而不是"爱"
But it's beauty, not love.

1045
01:21:56,350 --> 01:21:57,890
怎么了
What?

1046
01:22:01,110 --> 01:22:03,360
离午夜还差一分钟
It's a minute to midnight.

1047
01:22:06,090 --> 01:22:08,750
比我预想的还要早
Sooner than I expected.

1048
01:22:12,360 --> 01:22:14,310
我们要去哪
Where're we going?

1049
01:22:20,770 --> 01:22:22,310
噢
Oh.

1050
01:22:23,840 --> 01:22:25,910
我明白了
I see.

1051
01:22:28,380 --> 01:22:34,220
我们一同策划 一同构思
We planned it together, we designed it together,

1052
01:22:36,070 --> 01:22:38,590
但这部分只有你才知晓
but this part only belongs to you.

1053
01:22:38,610 --> 01:22:43,120
你不知道在哪 才会更安全
It's just safer if you don't know where.

1054
01:22:45,720 --> 01:22:48,230
如果他们抢先找到了你呢
What if they find you first?

1055
01:22:51,300 --> 01:22:53,130
那时怎么办
What then?

1056
01:22:57,400 --> 01:23:00,120
如果你想知道 你也不是一个人
If you want to know, you're not alone.

1057
01:23:01,190 --> 01:23:03,360
你得开始相信我
You got to start by trusting me.

1058
01:23:03,380 --> 01:23:06,510
我们若不立即采取大胆行动
Unless we take bold immediate action

1059
01:23:06,540 --> 01:23:11,390
第六次大灭绝就会轮到我们头上
the sixth extinction will be our own.

1060
01:23:24,010 --> 01:23:25,590
你说得对
You were right.

1061
01:23:28,540 --> 01:23:31,000
我要给你安排另一条路
I'm going to make you another path.

1062
01:23:33,190 --> 01:23:35,430
地狱也在尽头
Inferno will be at the end.

1063
01:23:35,460 --> 01:23:40,740
如果我遇到不测 第一条线索就会发给你
If something should happen to me, the first clue will be deliver to you.

1064
01:23:40,770 --> 01:23:43,700
我知道你会做好必须要做的事情
I know you'll do what must to be done.

1065
01:23:44,170 --> 01:23:46,300
寻找 就寻见
Seek and find.

1066
01:23:50,340 --> 01:23:52,290
你不是一个人
You're not alone.

1067
01:24:55,700 --> 01:24:57,370
那么
So.

1068
01:24:57,400 --> 01:25:00,980
漂亮的小妮子跑去找坏家伙了
The beautiful young woman went for the bad guy.

1069
01:25:01,860 --> 01:25:04,020
这事常常发生
That happens.

1070
01:25:05,240 --> 01:25:07,460
你看着好失望呢
You look disappointed.

1071
01:25:08,950 --> 01:25:10,540
我先让你缓一缓
I'll give you a minute.

1072
01:25:10,570 --> 01:25:15,560
伊丽莎白并非是想要转卖病毒的人
Elizabeth is not the one who wants the virus to sell.

1073
01:25:16,160 --> 01:25:17,880
那人是你
You are.

1074
01:25:18,780 --> 01:25:20,930
你被人利用了
You've been used.

1075
01:25:21,610 --> 01:25:26,430
有人在精心计划 驱使你为他们效力
Elaborate schemes created by people to get you to do what they want.

1076
01:25:27,920 --> 01:25:29,650
至于我
But me,

1077
01:25:31,330 --> 01:25:33,110
我就简单粗暴了
I'm very direct.

1078
01:25:33,140 --> 01:25:36,890
现在我正掌握一个绝佳的机会
And this is a moment of great opportunity for me.

1079
01:25:36,910 --> 01:25:40,170
所以 病毒在哪里
So, where is the virus?

1080
01:25:45,170 --> 01:25:47,370
拜托 教授
Come on, Professor.

1081
01:25:47,720 --> 01:25:50,410
人世间生命几何
How much life is there in the world?

1082
01:25:51,200 --> 01:25:54,140
有多少生来就在困苦挣扎
How much more is fighting to be born?

1083
01:25:56,660 --> 01:25:59,500
偶尔自相残杀也并无过错
Nothing wrong with thinning the herd once in a while.

1084
01:26:05,600 --> 01:26:06,900
很正常
It's healthy.

1085
01:26:09,410 --> 01:26:12,070
我已见过许多天意
I've seen many acts of god.

1086
01:26:12,170 --> 01:26:16,500
我是说 台风 霍乱 你知道吗
I mean, typhoons, cholera. And you know what?

1087
01:26:18,000 --> 01:26:20,700
有时候带走的 还是善人之命
Sometimes it hits the right people.

1088
01:26:21,480 --> 01:26:24,700
- 惨无人性 - 人之常情本就是不人道的
- That's inhuman. - Humanity is inhuman.

1089
01:26:25,200 --> 01:26:28,670
人命或许轻贱 但从未有人停止过
Life maybe cheap, but the means to end it on a mass scale,

1090
01:26:28,700 --> 01:26:31,050
探求灭绝众生的方法手段
no one ever stops paying for that.

1091
01:26:39,090 --> 01:26:41,700
我再最后问你一...
I'm going to ask you for the last...

1092
01:26:45,800 --> 01:26:47,890
万分抱歉
Terribly sorry.

1093
01:26:50,640 --> 01:26:52,630
没别的法子了
Didn't see any other way.

1094
01:26:53,840 --> 01:26:58,170
须得迅雷不及掩耳 见血越少 效果越好
Must do this quickly. The less blood the better.

1095
01:26:58,850 --> 01:27:00,620
你是哪位
Who are you?

1096
01:27:01,710 --> 01:27:04,310
噢 一名协作者
Oh, a facilitator.

1097
01:27:04,340 --> 01:27:07,550
除了别的业务 我们公司还制造幻觉
Among other things my company creates illusions.

1098
01:27:07,580 --> 01:27:09,980
你的头部并没有受伤
You never had a real head wound.

1099
01:27:12,270 --> 01:27:17,250
- 但我失忆了 - 是化学作用
- But I lost my memory. - Chemically induced.

1100
01:27:17,270 --> 01:27:20,910
我们给你注射的是苯二氮䓬类药物 (精神药物)
We gave you an injection of benzodiazapenes.

1101
01:27:21,310 --> 01:27:26,330
抱歉 会伴有皮疹 一两天后就消退
Sorry, it can produce a skin rash. It should fade in a day or so.

1102
01:27:29,770 --> 01:27:31,950
这些都是...
All this was a...

1103
01:27:31,970 --> 01:27:33,550
这些都是假的吗
All this was a fake?

1104
01:27:33,580 --> 01:27:36,650
我更喜欢制造真实感
I prefer created reality.

1105
01:27:36,670 --> 01:27:40,910
我的手下绑架了你
My agents kidnapped you.

1106
01:27:40,930 --> 01:27:44,650
为了触发全新的剧情 他们消去了你的记忆
They cleared your memories so we could create a fresh scenario,

1107
01:27:44,670 --> 01:27:48,490
由此你便投身于协助我们的思路中
whereby you would be invested in the idea of helping us.

1108
01:27:49,600 --> 01:27:55,280
我们在你头皮上划了一道小口子 这是枪击幻觉的一部分
A small incision was made in your scalp to give the impression of a bullet graze.

1109
01:27:56,870 --> 01:27:59,420
医院里的门也是假锁的
There are no locks on hospital doors.

1110
01:27:59,450 --> 01:28:01,070
没错
Exactly.

1111
01:28:01,180 --> 01:28:02,490
满分回答
Highest marks.

1112
01:28:02,510 --> 01:28:05,970
医院里杀人的那位女警察呢
What about the policewoman who shot the Doctor in the hospital?

1113
01:28:06,000 --> 01:28:07,240
也是我的人
Also it's me.

1114
01:28:07,260 --> 01:28:09,000
她的枪里是空包弹
Her gun fired blanks.

1115
01:28:09,520 --> 01:28:11,750
门上则有爆炸伪造的枪击效果
And there were squibs in the door.

1116
01:28:11,770 --> 01:28:13,850
医生是演员 身上挂着袋血浆包
The doctor was an agent wearing a blood packet.

1117
01:28:13,870 --> 01:28:17,830
出租车司机 整个医院都是咱们的人
The taxi driver, the hospital was working for us as well.

1118
01:28:18,200 --> 01:28:21,050
在旧宫里她试图要杀了我
At the Palazzo Vecchio she tried to kill me.

1119
01:28:21,630 --> 01:28:23,530
那是真枪实弹
It was real bullets.

1120
01:28:24,120 --> 01:28:26,070
我要求的
At my behest.

1121
01:28:26,090 --> 01:28:28,520
当事情快要败露时
When things that appeared to go tits up

1122
01:28:28,540 --> 01:28:30,670
我会试图赶紧杀人灭口 毁尸灭迹
I try to sweep it all away quickly.

1123
01:28:30,700 --> 01:28:31,970
所以要杀我
By killing me?

1124
01:28:32,000 --> 01:28:35,650
我深表歉意 兰登先生
I apologize unreservedly, Mr. Langdon.

1125
01:28:42,680 --> 01:28:45,220
我的确失去了一名老部下
I did lose an experienced agent.

1126
01:28:46,530 --> 01:28:50,530
这个行当里 我见过的情况够多了
There's a great deal of situation I've been informed in my line of work.

1127
01:28:52,290 --> 01:28:55,080
瞧 我知道的就这些
Look, hear me what I know.

1128
01:28:55,110 --> 01:28:57,630
我知道我看着很渗人
I know I've behaved terribly.

1129
01:29:00,620 --> 01:29:05,350
但谜题需要破解 这一点你最棒了
But a puzzle needed solving, who better to solve it than you.

1130
01:29:05,920 --> 01:29:07,790
瞟一眼 好吗
Glance at it, will you?

1131
01:29:21,220 --> 01:29:23,450
干得差强人意了
Not my best work.

1132
01:29:24,040 --> 01:29:26,700
但足以应付意大利人
But it will do for the Italians.

1133
01:29:27,590 --> 01:29:32,720
西恩娜来找我求助的时候 佐布里斯特早已拥趸者众
Zobrist had followers everywhere when Sienna first came to me for help.

1134
01:29:32,750 --> 01:29:34,710
至少我是这么认为的
Or so I thought.

1135
01:29:34,730 --> 01:29:39,320
佐布里斯特死后不久 她就很严肃地找上门来
She came to us with serious concerns shortly after Zobrist died.

1136
01:29:40,400 --> 01:29:43,570
不知怎的 她知道了我们受雇于佐布里斯特
Somehow, she knew Zobrist had hired us.

1137
01:29:43,600 --> 01:29:47,240
她表示这位富翁的生物研究成果 可能已经落到坏人手中
She said he was doing biological work that could be fallen into the wrong hands.

1138
01:29:47,270 --> 01:29:50,420
她并未提及瘟疫 但我们已经开始警惕
She didn't mention a plague. But we heard enough to be alarmed.

1139
01:29:50,450 --> 01:29:54,320
于是我们同意协助她 找到佐布里斯特的计划
So we agreed to work with her to find Zobrist's project.

1140
01:29:54,350 --> 01:29:58,980
然后当辛斯基博士带你来时 我们看到了机会
And when Dr. Sinskey brought you in, we saw an opportunity.

1141
01:29:59,010 --> 01:30:01,250
当时是伊丽莎白来找我的
It was Elizabeth who came to see me.

1142
01:30:01,280 --> 01:30:02,600
是的
Yes.

1143
01:30:02,630 --> 01:30:06,570
从布沙尔探员手上 辛斯基博士弄到了法拉第指示器
Dr. Sinskey got the Faraday pointer from agent Bouchard.

1144
01:30:06,600 --> 01:30:08,820
她带去让你解密
She brought it to you to decode,

1145
01:30:08,840 --> 01:30:11,670
甚至用你的指纹来设作密码
and she even secured it with your thumbprint.

1146
01:30:11,700 --> 01:30:13,120
我们别无选择
That left us with no choice,

1147
01:30:13,140 --> 01:30:15,780
所以我们在街上把你抢了过来
so we took you from her on the street.

1148
01:30:17,620 --> 01:30:21,870
医院里的情况促使你相信布鲁克斯医生
The hospital scenario encouraged you to trust Dr. Brooks.

1149
01:30:21,900 --> 01:30:26,410
你们给领事馆打电话时 另一头接通的是我们
When you called to the Consulate it was answered by our man.

1150
01:30:26,430 --> 01:30:27,940
兰登教授
Professor Langdon?

1151
01:30:27,960 --> 01:30:30,600
谢天谢地你还活着 我们一直在找你
Thank heavens you're alive. We've been looking for you.

1152
01:30:30,630 --> 01:30:31,920
东西你还带着吗
Are you still in possession?

1153
01:30:31,950 --> 01:30:33,980
你带着指示器 我们跟着你
You had the pointer and we had you.

1154
01:30:34,000 --> 01:30:37,890
一切都推进的天衣无缝 直到布鲁克斯女士把你引开
It was all working seamlessly until Miss. Brooks stole you away.

1155
01:30:37,920 --> 01:30:41,120
以确保病毒得以释放
To make sure the virus is released.

1156
01:30:42,200 --> 01:30:44,150
看来
It appears.

1157
01:30:44,860 --> 01:30:47,530
年轻人很失望
Young people are disappointing.

1158
01:30:48,940 --> 01:30:52,410
我发现他们35岁左右时 就挺有耐性的了
I find them become tolerable around 35.

1159
01:30:54,970 --> 01:30:57,360
你提到过辛斯基博士
You mentioed Dr. Sinskey.

1160
01:31:04,920 --> 01:31:07,000
我一直很担心你
I've been so worried.

1161
01:31:08,550 --> 01:31:10,300
你还好吗
Are you alright?

1162
01:31:10,330 --> 01:31:12,630
- 我很好 - 是吗
- I'm fine. - Are you?

1163
01:31:12,650 --> 01:31:14,450
我很好
I'm okay.

1164
01:31:14,920 --> 01:31:16,720
挺好的
I'm alright.

1165
01:31:17,850 --> 01:31:19,530
谢天谢地
Thank god.

1166
01:31:22,000 --> 01:31:25,250
- 你知道病毒在哪儿吗 - 伊斯坦布尔
- Do you know where the virus is? - Istanbul.

1167
01:31:26,160 --> 01:31:29,300
世界卫生组织专机 下午 5:32

1168
01:31:29,800 --> 01:31:31,800
现在正是时候
Now's the time.

1169
01:31:32,270 --> 01:31:34,540
今天是重生之日
Today is rebirth.

1170
01:31:34,750 --> 01:31:37,120
地狱就是救赎
Inferno is salvation.

1171
01:31:42,690 --> 01:31:45,110
我很抱歉把你卷进来 罗伯特
I am so sorry I brought you into this, Robert,

1172
01:31:45,130 --> 01:31:49,620
- 在这么多年之后 - 没事 我很高兴你那么做了
- after all these years. - No. I'm glad you did.

1173
01:31:50,120 --> 01:31:53,680
我见过他 佐布里斯特 两年前
I met him, you know. Zobrist, 2 years ago.

1174
01:31:53,710 --> 01:31:55,440
他当时向我求助
He asked for my help.

1175
01:31:55,460 --> 01:31:58,780
他想让WHO支持他的行动
He wanted the WHO to endorse mass sterilization

1176
01:31:58,810 --> 01:32:01,420
对饮用水和主食中进行大规模杀菌消毒
in drinking waters and staple foods.

1177
01:32:01,440 --> 01:32:05,590
于是我下了逐客令 把他列为监控对像
So I threw him out of my office, put him on the watch list.

1178
01:32:06,440 --> 01:32:08,790
但他失踪了...
But he disappeared and...

1179
01:32:10,450 --> 01:32:13,990
我猜那就是他雇佣了西姆斯的时候
I suppose that's when Zobrist hired Sims.

1180
01:32:14,750 --> 01:32:19,030
我早应该发... 我不知道
I should probably have... have I don't know.

1181
01:32:19,050 --> 01:32:19,810
怎么
What?

1182
01:32:19,830 --> 01:32:24,300
这些都不是你的错 你总要为它们责怪自己
You always blame yourself for things that weren't your fault.

1183
01:32:26,200 --> 01:32:28,500
嘴还是很甜
Still very sweet.

1184
01:32:44,860 --> 01:32:47,190
这边 有个门口
Here, a doorway.

1185
01:32:58,670 --> 01:33:02,710
我希望见面那会 是别的事情呢
I wish it would have happened differently, back then.

1186
01:33:04,630 --> 01:33:08,550
咱们当时没有经营好 就这么散了
We didn't look after it. It fell apart.

1187
01:33:08,900 --> 01:33:10,830
这算是后悔吗
Is that a regret?

1188
01:33:13,080 --> 01:33:15,450
我想起来的时候才会这样
Only when I think about it.

1189
01:33:21,430 --> 01:33:24,890
你知道吗 在门口那发生的最有意思的事情是
You know, the most interesting things happened in doorways,

1190
01:33:25,100 --> 01:33:29,140
那样一种持续的临界状态
at the borders, right along the edges.

1191
01:33:31,240 --> 01:33:36,000
古代渔民会在寒暖洋流交汇处打渔
Ancient fishermen learned to sail where the warm water met the cold.

1192
01:33:36,030 --> 01:33:40,410
小鱼会滞留在暖流边上
The little fish would reach the edge of the warm water and they stopped.

1193
01:33:40,440 --> 01:33:43,350
然后大鱼就从寒流里游过来 把它们吃掉
And the big fish would come out of the cold water and they eat them.

1194
01:33:43,380 --> 01:33:45,810
最后是渔民们
And the fishermen.

1195
01:33:46,210 --> 01:33:48,480
嗯 渔翁得利
Well, they caught everybody.

1196
01:33:53,280 --> 01:33:54,990
门口那儿
Doorways.

1197
01:33:57,470 --> 01:34:01,610
你还是老样子 罗伯特
Not one part of you has changed, Robert.

1198
01:34:04,880 --> 01:34:07,250
话痨一个
You talk too much.

1199
01:34:08,960 --> 01:34:13,570
嗯 一点也没变
And then, not at all

1200
01:34:14,390 --> 01:34:16,070
伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

1201
01:34:17,700 --> 01:34:23,380
我无法请求你别去日内瓦
I couldn't ask you not to go to Geneva.

1202
01:34:25,500 --> 01:34:26,900
做不到
I couldn't.

